OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry, sunny and hot
OL,6,Fday today, although a small chance of
OL,7,Fa few showers developing along the
OL,8,Fsouth coast later. Widely breezy with
OL,9,Fstrong winds continuing along the
OL,10,Fsouth coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA risk of some further
OL,13,Fshowers towards Devon and Cornwall
OL,14,Fthis evening. Otherwise a warm but dry
OL,15,Fnight with plenty of clear skies.
OL,16,FStaying breezy near the south coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
