OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAnother hot day on Tuesday,
OL,6,Falthough sunshine likely to be more
OL,7,Fhazy than of late. A small chance of
OL,8,Fthe odd shower in the west but most
OL,9,Fstaying dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FRemaining hot with plenty more
OL,13,Fsunshine, although an increasing risk
OL,14,Fof some showers and thunderstorms at
OL,15,Ftimes. Lighter winds than Monday and
OL,16,FTuesday adding to the hot feel.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
